Class Professor

java.lang.Object
  teachersV2.Professor

public class Professor
extends java.lang.Object

The professor can put marks to students depending of the promotion, the id of the student and if he wants to add/modify a mark.

setNote

public void setNote(Promotion p,
                    int id,
                    float value,
                    int index)
Set or Modify a mark depending of the student's array. - Set : If no marks is in the specified index, we add the new mark in the array. - Modify : If a mark does exist in a index of the student's array, we modify it with the new value.

Parameters:
p - The Promotion where student is.
id - The identifying student.
value - The value of the mark.
index - The index in the student's array
